ass=\"red\"><strong>0.056%/0.000196%=286，即係出街比狗殺既機會係撞到逃跑病人而中招死既286倍</strong></span>，舊年都唔怕死，今年怕隻廢病，仲要一齊通緝捉人無視人權，如果要驚既咁不如唔好出街，成世匿係屋企等光復到香港先好出黎，都唔好再話自己係咩19抗爭者，你只係連屬於緊急法/惡法既防疫條例都擁護既建制派<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/2976970\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2976970&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=00d9962d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/2976970</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=365778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365778&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=8727a947\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365778&h=87e60a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=365778</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chp-dashboard.geodata.gov.hk/covid-19/zh.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchp-dashboard.geodata.gov.hk%2Fcovid-19%2Fzh.html&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=b8df0af0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chp-dashboard.geodata.gov.hk/covid-19/zh.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T08:09:00.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"4100e5e605797e8d08ff3384d6228f264dcf6e20","tid":2344992,"uid":254497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a702a002bd197b185b52cd99634a1b932a09d0e6","tid":2344992,"uid":54791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da17929714dd961666b4a07ef50496ebf91fc992","tid":2344992,"uid":254497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19c7f64ea0fe42ba15e85b8e66cb5e9d6a5a274b","tid":2344992,"uid":54791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"repl